    "description": "在这里，史诗般的冒险与策略卡牌对战交相辉映。登上传说之塔，打造自己的卡组，对抗可怕的怪物，创造自己的命运。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/e860f12dc1d7f031b92b1f25bba098a3.apng?t=1751281912\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/e860f12dc1d7f031b92b1f25bba098a3.poster.avif?t=1751281912\" class=\"bb_img\" width=618 height=32 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >卡牌中的生命</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/cbbabf133cd3bb55a0df2bce0878e529.poster.avif?t=1751281912\" width=618 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/cbbabf133cd3bb55a0df2bce0878e529.webm?t=1751281912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/8bacd49cb90dcbea980597562a1ec7d3.poster.avif?t=1751281912\" width=618 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/8bacd49cb90dcbea980597562a1ec7d3.webm?t=1751281912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>健康是游戏中的宝贵资源。每出一张牌都会消耗您的健康值，因此每一个决定都是一场高风险的赌博。明智地选择你的行动，因为你必须在力量和保护之间取得平衡。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的卡组构建</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/a6d946f722cfd90eea3003374ac9bb43.poster.avif?t=1751281912\" width=618 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/a6d946f722cfd90eea3003374ac9bb43.webm?t=1751281912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在旅途中收集大量卡牌，每张卡牌都有自己的能力和后果。您的卡组将随着您的进程不断演变，反映出您角色的成长和适应能力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >改变规则</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/484b8324d3d9ddd8a8be4ea52d1b1ee7.poster.avif?t=1751281912\" width=618 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/484b8324d3d9ddd8a8be4ea52d1b1ee7.webm?t=1751281912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>使用世界卡牌改变游戏规则，突袭地牢。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >难度可变</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/516679d40d6271e2a52e7d2069215d69.poster.avif?t=1751281912\" width=618 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/516679d40d6271e2a52e7d2069215d69.webm?t=1751281912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>确保新手和老手都能玩这款游戏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >按程序生成的楼层</h2>准备好迎接不断变化的挑战吧。通天塔的每一层都是按程序生成的，确保没有两次运行是相同的。揭开隐藏的秘密，发现新的策略，面对无法预料的障碍。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >清新的艺术风格</h2>在 3D 世界中实现复古像素艺术。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/e860f12dc1d7f031b92b1f25bba098a3.apng?t=1751281912\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/e860f12dc1d7f031b92b1f25bba098a3.poster.avif?t=1751281912\" class=\"bb_img\" width=618 height=32 /></picture></span>",
